Computers are used to solve specific problems. We can write programs to solve some of the problems faced by an ATC.

ATC has to solve many problems as mentioned below.

Can you connect the below questions to the mentioned categories of problems using the mouse?



How many flights have landed today?           Counting

Should a flight land immediately or 
circle in air for some more time?             Decision

Which runway is currently free? 		          Searching

Among the many flights ready for 
landing, the flight with the lowest 
fuel level should be allowed to land 
first. How can it be done?                    Sorting

1200 landings and takeoffs happen in
a day with only 2 runways. How do you
manage it? 		 		                            Optimization
